msgid ""
"Displays the health of all ZFS pools with traffic-light status. Green = "
"healthy, orange = >80% full, red = degraded/faulted/errors/>90% full. Click "
"a pool to view details."
msgstr "以交通號誌來顯示全部 ZFS 集用場的健康狀況。綠 = 健康，橘 = >80% 滿，紅 = 降級/故障/錯誤/>90% 滿。點選一個集用場來檢視詳情。"

msgid ""
"Do not create a new snapshot. Instead, replicate the most recent existing "
"snapshot matching the prefix. Use this when a separate snapshot job already "
"manages snapshots for this dataset — this is the recommended approach when "
"replicating to multiple destinations or at different frequencies, as it "
"avoids conflicts between replication chains."
msgstr "不要產生新的快照。而是複製符合前綴詞的現存最新快照。當另一個快照工作已經在為此資料集管理快照時，就可使用這個 — 當複製到多個目的地或以不同的頻率做複製，這是推薦的作法，因為它能避免複製鍊間的衝突。"

